The eastern portion of this area is somewhat barren, but the trees thicken
moving west, especially to the northwest. Most of the ground here is firm
and solid, but a bit softer to the east. Most of the vegetation here is
maples and elms.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT E 3034
EXIT S 3038
